INSERT INTO UserTankCustomizations (user_id, tank_id=0, weapon_id, slot_position=0)
SELECT tw.*, utc.tank_id, utc.slot_position FROM TankWeapons tw LEFT JOIN UserTankCustomizations utc ON tw.id = utc.weapon_id AND utc.user_id = ?
{armi: [{id: 1, name: "Cannone Base", posseduta: true, equipaggiata_su: [1,2]}, {id: 3, name: "Mitragliatrice Pesante", posseduta: true, equipaggiata_su: []}]}
INSERT INTO UserTankCustomizations (user_id, tank_id, weapon_id, slot_position) ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE weapon_id = VALUES(weapon_id)
UPDATE UserTankCustomizations SET weapon_id = ? WHERE user_id = ? AND tank_id = ? AND slot_position = ?
SELECT utc.slot_position, tw.* FROM UserTankCustomizations utc JOIN TankWeapons tw ON utc.weapon_id = tw.id WHERE utc.user_id = ? AND utc.tank_id = ? AND utc.slot_position > 0
{loadout: [{slot: 1, arma: {id: 1, name: "Cannone Base", type: "cannon", damage: 100}}, {slot: 2, arma: {id: 3, name: "Mitragliatrice Pesante", type: "machine_gun", damage: 40}}]}
